  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watermelon Simulator is a game in which you can become a watermelon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game will give you a meditative gameplay. You can stand and contemplate the beauty of the town around you living your life as a watermelon. You can also perform actions that watermelons usually perform (stand in the same place). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a watermelon </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're on the table</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are other watermelons around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And not only watermelons</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 game mods: arcade and realistic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic graphics</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watermelon Simulator is a game in which you can become a watermelon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game will give you a meditative gameplay. You can stand and contemplate the beauty of the town around you living your life as a watermelon. You can also perform actions that watermelons usually perform (stand in the same place). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a watermelon </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're on the table</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are other watermelons around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And not only watermelons</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 game mods: arcade and realistic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic graphics</p></li></ul>",
